       /'COR replacement will cost you P280.00',                                                                                 /125 'Add on: Installment Fee',                        155 f_addon.

SKIP.
SKIP.
WRITE:                /17 u_fullname_2,
                      /17 SY-ULINE(20),                                                      75'College Registrar',
                      /18'Student Signature'.

